      "settings": {
        "kicker": "Davines",
        "title": "Davines NaturalTech Purifying",
        "text": "<p>Eliminate dandruff and restore a healthy scalp with Davines' anti-dandruff treatments. Malassezia globosa lives on your scalp, feeding on skin's oils, causing dandruff and potentially leading to hair loss. All natural, active ingredients are rich in antioxidants and possess anti-inflammatory and antibacterial properties to revitalize the scalp. <br/><a href=\"/collections/davines\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Davines\"><strong>Davines</strong></a><strong> </strong>products are paraben and sulfate free. Made with ingredients of natural origin, sourced from organic farms.</p>",
