            "kicker": "Davines NaturalTech Purifying Shampoo",
            "title": "",
            "text": "<h2><a href=\"/pages/effective-dandruff-solution-davines\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Effective Dandruff Solution: Davines Purifying & Well-Being\">Effective Dandruff Solution</a></h2><p>Tame dandruff with Davines Purifying Shampoo—soothing dry, itchy scalps while tackling flakes. Ideal for oily or dry dandruff, scalp psoriasis, and seborrheic dermatitis, it clears the scalp without harsh chemicals.</p><p>Use <strong>twice a week for up to 3 weeks</strong>, then <strong>once weekly for up to 6 weeks</strong> or until resolved. Apply to a wet scalp, leave for 3 minutes, then rinse. For best results, alternate with Davines <a href=\"/products/davines-renewing-shampoo\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Davines Renewing Shampoo: Longevity for All Scalp and Hair Types\">Renewing</a> or <a href=\"/products/davines-naturaltech-well-being-shampoo-for-all-kinds-of-hair\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Davines Well-Being Shampoo: Hydrating Shampoo For All Kinds of Hair\">Well-Being Shampoo</a>.</p>",
